# SolPredict ‚Äî Solana Devnet Prediction Market (No-Code Friendly)

A simple Yes/No prediction market dApp built on Solana Devnet using Next.js, React, TailwindCSS, and Phantom wallet.  
Perfect for hackathons. No on-chain program required.

---

## ‚ú® Features
- Phantom Wallet connect (Devnet)
- YES/NO voting interface
- Votes submitted as real Solana Devnet transactions
- Clean, minimal codebase
- Easy to deploy (Vercel)

